	<div class="entry-content">
		<p><!-- Tool Design :: Press Forming :: Extrusion :: Extrude :: Extruders :: Extruding :: Cold Heading :: Cold Forming :: Metal Forming :: Metal Flow :: Tooling :: Carbide :: Carbide Insert :: Die :: Design :: Engineering :: Engineering Consulting :: Engineering Design :: Die Design :: Tool and Die Design :: Tool Die Design :: Tool Die Layout and Design :: Tool Manufacturing :: Tool and Die Manufacturing :: Formax :: Automotive :: Cold Header :: Cold Header Tooling :: Fastener Tooling :: Cold Heading Wire :: Fasteners :: Extrusion Tooling :: Heading :: Cold Forging :: Tool Die :: Tool and Die // cold heading consulting :: cold forming consulting :: press forming consulting :: advance tool and die :: advanced cold forming :: advanced cold forming llc :: advanced cold forming te :: advanced tool and die :: advanced tool design :: aluminum cold forming :: black forest cold forming :: buy cold heading wire :: cold engineering :: cold extruding dies :: cold forging :: cold form :: cold formed extrusion pr :: cold formed special :: cold forming :: cold forming and metal :: cold forming dies :: cold forming engineer :: cold forming knowledges :: cold forming machinery :: cold forming machines :: cold forming metal :: cold forming metal :: cold forming press :: cold forming presses :: cold forming processes :: cold forming threads ins :: cold forming tool :: cold forming uk :: cold header :: cold header :: cold header dies :: cold header experience :: cold header tool :: cold header tooling :: cold headers :: cold heading :: cold heading :: cold heading china :: cold heading companies :: cold heading company :: cold heading company :: cold heading company us :: cold heading costs :: cold heading design :: cold heading die :: cold heading dies :: cold heading industry co :: cold heading jobs :: cold heading machines :: cold heading steel :: cold heading tooling :: cold heading tools :: cold heading wire :: cold-forming :: die formers :: engineering die design :: fasteners development co :: fea simulation :: formax :: forming metal :: header tooling :: how to design cold forging :: indiana cold form tooling :: involute :: jobs in heading cold forming :: linear cold forming light :: membrane press forming :: metal forming industry :: metal forming tool :: metal forming tools :: nakashimada parts :: national cold form tooling :: national cold formers :: national machine :: national machine progress :: national machinery :: national machinery forming :: national progressive headers :: ohio engineering manager :: part development :: part formers :: press forming :: sacma :: sacma multi die :: sacme :: sakamura :: sheet metal forming tool :: simulation :: single component cold forming :: spline :: tool and die :: tool and die design :: tool die design :: waterbury farrel rod heading :: Cold Former Michigan, Cold Forming Michigan, Cold Heading Michigan, MI, Tool and Die Shop Michigan, Die Making Michigan, Enginering Firm Michigan, Engineering Services Michigan, Extruder Michigan, Extrusions Michigan, Cold Former Michigan, Heading, Die Making Michigan, Extrusion, Four-Slide, Progressive, Stamping, Engineering Services Michigan, Analysis / Testing, CAD Services, CAM Services, Product Design, Reverse Engineering, Tool/Machinery Design, Extrusions Michigan, Alabama, Alaska ,Alberta, Arizona, Arkansas , British, California ,Colorado ,Connecticut ,Delaware ,Florida ,Georgia ,Hawaii, Idaho ,Illinois ,Indiana, Iowa ,Kansas ,Kentucky, Louisiana ,Maine ,Manitoba, Maryland ,Massachusetts ,Michigan ,Minnesota ,Mississippi ,Missouri, Montana ,Nebraska ,Nevada, New Hampshire ,New Jersey ,New Mexico ,New York ,Newfoundland, North Carolina ,North Dakota ,Ohio, Oklahoma ,Ontario,Oregon, Pennsylvania ,Rhode Island ,Saskatchewan, South Carolina ,South Dakota, Tennessee ,Texas ,Utah ,Vermont, Virginia ,Washington, Washington D.C ,West Virginia ,Wisconsin ,Wyoming, AL AK AZ AR CA CO CT DE FL GA HI ID IL IN IA KS KY LA ME MD MA MI MN MS MO MT NE NV NH NJ NM NY NC ND OH OK OR PA RI SC SD TN TX UT VT VA WA DC WV WI WY, Form Flow, Alken Ziegler and much more... metal forming simulation :: forming simulation :: simufact :: simufact forming :: deform :: metal forming software :: metal forming simulation software--></p>
<p><strong>&#8230;Where advanced technology, knowledge and proven experience drives results.</strong><br />
ACF was established to provide the cold forming industry with<strong> professional engineering support</strong> on all brands of machines as <strong>our main product</strong>. We specialize in helping customers take it to the next level in cold forming&#8230;.</p>
<p>ACF is <strong>supported by decades of TOOL DESIGN engineering and PART DEVELOPMENT experience</strong> in the cold forming industry.</p>
<p><strong>Aware of how dies fail in production, we draw from a wealth of experience to create greater production efficiency through a combination of proven tool design techniques and the art of a balanced and well thought out forming sequence.</strong>  We design tools that can be manufactured at a reasonable price and believe will provide you with improved tool life<strong>.</strong></p>
<p><strong>Optional 2D and 3D metal forming simulations are both available for forming sequence analysis</strong>. All ACF designs are fully modeled and assembled in 3D for accuracy before they are manufactured. Our overall process results in less time required grooming the tools the first time installed in your machine.</p>
<p>We offer customers the choice to order tools from your tool supplier or ACF can recommend a qualified supplier. Options for part development assistance are available on all jobs. <strong>Complete tool drawing packages are also available for those customers who want to buy engineering services only</strong>.</p>
<p><center><b><span style="color: #ff0000;"> Contact us to discuss your projects</span></b></center></p>
